Project 1 Idea

Community service event app - Users can post/edit events

Users can sign up and log in.

Users can post their events to the app.

Info to add: Event name, date, motivation



Sprint: Set up development environment - done

Sprint: Serve and render hard-coded data on the page, then connect to a database to show events index - done

- User can see an image with title of website and background image
- User can see a list of events with their respective info



Sprint: Add a form and support creating data

- User can see a form for searching for adding events
- User can type data in form
- User can click on button to add form info to database
- User can see an updated list of events

Sprint: Delete event

- User can see a delete button for each event
- User can click on button to delete event
- User can see updated page data

Sprint: Edit and update customized event info

- User can see an edit button for each event
- User can click on button to enable making changes to certain event input fields
- User can type changes to event info
- User can click on button to update event info
- User can see updated page data